,"updatedAt":1776135836215,"sessionId":"ec66ca1c-2f81-42a4-8b31-c1b413ee1712","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":35818,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"timeout","startedAt":1776134770702,"endedAt":1776135674111,"runtimeMs":0,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ec66ca1c-2f81-42a4-8b31-c1b413ee1712.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776135774216,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"22bb3dab","seq":133}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776135792089,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"e6a6b4e3","seq":134}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776135807578,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"c08bc1f3","seq":135}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:2e5ea409-572b-4929-8001-fa602be9c6d2","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"dtlx:module1-auth","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776131259293,"sessionId":"523f0300-39cc-4a2a-a793-4bca4ce57459","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776131213350,"endedAt":1776131244274,"runtimeMs":30924,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/523f0300-39cc-4a2a-a793-4bca4ce57459.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are senior-backend. Test Module 1: AUTH API for ahv-dtlx-backend.\n\n## Context\n- Workspace: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n- Server port: 5555\n- Label: dtlx:auth-test\n\n## Steps\n\n### 1. Setup\n- cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n- cp .env.example .env  (if .env doesn't exist)\n- Run: yarn seed  (seeds admin account admin123@gmail.com / 123456)\n- Start server: yarn dev  (background)\n- Wait for server to start (look for \"listening\" or \"started\")\n\n### 2. Test AUTH endpoints (PUBLIC - no token needed)\nUse curl to test each endpoint:\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/auth/login\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\", \"password\": \"123456\" }\nExpected: JWT token\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/register  \nBody: { \"email\": \"test@test.com\", \"password\": \"123456\", \"name\": \"Test User\" }\nExpected: user created\n\nGET /api/v1/auth/me\nExpected: current user info (if authenticated)\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\" }\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/refresh\n```\n\n### 3. After login success\n- Save the JWT token from login response\n- Test GET /api/v1/auth/me with the token (Authorization: Bearer <token>)\n\n### 4. Report\nFor EACH endpoint, report:\n- ✅ /api/v1/auth/xxx — HTTP status, response (truncated if long)\n- ❌ /api/v1/auth/xxx — HTTP status, error message\n\n## Rules\n- Read-only API testing\n- NEVER push or commit code\n- Kill background server when done"}],"timestamp":1776131231850,"__openclaw":{"id":"4b8eb889","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131231877,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"5afe1e66","seq":2}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131239731,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"55a05b1d","seq":3}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:e3ca11a2-c1e6-4d1d-9d7c-680d2d0d259a","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"dtlx:api-test","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776131199486,"sessionId":"b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":13326,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"killed","startedAt":1776130995085,"endedAt":1776131198083,"runtimeMs":120587,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":true,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The seed command doesn't exist. Let me check the package.json for available scripts."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rp80wdcy1t2g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat package.json | grep -A 30 '\"scripts\"'","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":141,"output":83,"totalTokens":13409,"cacheRead":12917,"cacheWrite":268,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776131191078,"responseId":"062ccf78fa2ef02cf530584ff3ea9ac7","__openclaw":{"id":"726c10f3","seq":17}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776131194520,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"9285c51d","seq":19}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776117647627,"sessionId":"ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":17388,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the latest memory file for today's context."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ibqpnivm2tg0_1","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-04-13.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2864,"output":47,"totalTokens":17165,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":310,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776117667835,"responseId":"062c9aa47d68f42fe912777fc540e234","__openclaw":{"id":"fbd26372","seq":5}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context to compose the daily briefing. Let me craft a clean status report for the Telegram group -5212380728.\n\nKey info:\n- Yesterday (2026-04-12): AHV Works review complete, session crash and recovery, BE behind 11 commits, FE synced\n- Today (2026-04-13): Fix AHV Works P0 issues (13 items), Stitch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\n\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"🌅 **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\n📅 Monday, April 13, 2026\n⏰ 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**1️⃣ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\n✅ **AHV Works Review** — FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\n✅ **Session Recovery** — Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n✅ **FE Sync** — Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop ✅\n✅ **DTLX/QLHV Systems** — Stable, shared DB architecture operational\n✅ **34-Agent Ecosystem** — SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified ✅\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**2️⃣ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\n🔴 **P0 — AHV Works Fixes** — 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\n🟡 **Stitch MCP Wrapper** — Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\n🟡 **stitch-connect Skill** — Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\n🔵 **BE Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nOrbis 🌐 — Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776117671474,"responseId":"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f","__openclaw":{"id":"faf39631","seq":7}}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776207251263}}
